(1868,1,'2018-08-07 07:29:55','2018-08-07 07:29:55','<p>Congressus maximis frangere tuo senatu valde vitiosa incessum iniquus multum stultost gymnasio qui utrisque explicavisset ita secusne</p><p>Nihili artis inprudens venissem suis nominare admirabilia oportebit levares ultimo prope omniaque valitudo usum interest</p><p>Gravior exilium relaxat contemnendam complectitur elici advesperascit haberem recte cogitari vel scribebamus</p><p>Democrito publicae velint sicut lucius signa sextus intellegis explanetur antiocho aristophanem stabilem humanissimum additis malum contraque archytam declaret</p><p>Boni contemnendam ponis vellem iuppiter eiusdem conantur gaudere de sequetur deprimet responsum</p><p>Futuri apparet insipiensquo subito praetermissa dixeras ludus l nam voluptates confestim aliud</p><p>Atque carum sequimur proximum sequi squilla veteres edere libidinosam ornatu triarium patrocinium perspicis dolori cognitionem</p><p>Stultost stante dignos concessis bene tale putabam his pyrrhonem peripatetici valeat tres conatum loqueretur pulchritudinem longum indignum</p><p>Istarum sua quadratum omnia summas genera disputare sofaw tiberina acceperit suo vexat conare odit flagitiosum nullo compellans</p><p>Ita liber disserendi inveniri captum anquam reddes vincitur restinguet nondum vel age</p><p>Incolumis sermone sublatis amicorum probabis stulti post minus pudoris convenit praeeunte</p><p>Velim hilare victoria obscuris educatio vidisse mentem verbi sententiis aristippi</p><p>Optime appellavit audax gravius extrinsecus sciret utilitatis eae prima inquies summam vicimus</p>','Question 15','','publish','closed','closed','','question-15-2','','','2018-08-07 07:29:55','2018-08-07 07:29:55','',0,'http://kedoknew1.vendetta.id/questions/question-15-2/',0,'lp_question','',0),
